---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Translation by Industry â€“ Legal, Healthcare, Real Estate, E-Commerce | OnlineTranslation.ae"
  description="Specialized translation services for different industries in the UAE. Legal, healthcare, real estate, and e-commerce expertise with MOJ certification."
>
  <section class="hero-section bg-dark" data-theme="dark">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">HOME</a>
        <span class="separator">&gt;</span>
        <span class="current">INDUSTRIES</span>
      </nav>
      
      <h1>Translation by Industry</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Specialized Expertise for Your Sector</p>
      <p class="hero-intro">Different industries have different requirements. Legal terminology for law firms, medical precision for healthcare, property jargon for real estate, and commercial language for e-commerce. We understand the nuances that make translations work for your specific sector.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Professional Services</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Precision translation for regulated industries.</p>
      
      <div class="service-grid">
        <a href="/industries/legal/" class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-gavel"></i></div>
          <h3>Legal and Law Firms</h3>
          <p>Court documents, contracts, litigation support, and case materials for law practices and corporate legal departments.</p>
        </a>
        
        <a href="/industries/healthcare/" class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-heartbeat"></i></div>
          <h3>Healthcare</h3>
          <p>Medical reports, clinical documents, insurance claims, and healthcare provider communications.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Commercial Sectors</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Business-focused translation for commercial operations.</p>
      
      <div class="service-grid">
        <a href="/industries/real-estate/" class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-home"></i></div>
          <h3>Real Estate</h3>
          <p>Property contracts, title deeds, SPA agreements, and developer documentation for investors and agents.</p>
        </a>
        
        <a href="/industries/e-commerce/" class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i></div>
          <h3>E-Commerce</h3>
          <p>Terms of service, product documentation, supplier agreements, and international trade documents.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container cta-section">
      <h2>Industry-Specific Requirements?</h2>
      <p>Tell us about your sector and document types. We will advise on the specific terminology, formatting, and certification requirements for your industry.</p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/971508620217" class="btn btn-primary">
        <i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i> Discuss Your Industry Needs
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero-section {
    padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
    background: var(--primary-color);
  }
  
  .breadcrumb {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .breadcrumb a {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  
  .breadcrumb a:hover {
    color: #ffffff;
  }
  
  .breadcrumb .separator {
    margin: 0 0.5rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  }
  
  .breadcrumb .current {
    color: #ffffff;
  }
  
  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #ffffff;
  }
  
  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--accent-color);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .hero-intro {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 700px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  }
  
  .section-intro {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .service-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .service-card {
    background: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .service-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    border-color: var(--accent-color);
  }
  
  .bg-light .service-card {
    background: #ffffff;
  }
  
  .service-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: var(--primary-color);
    color: #ffffff;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  
  .service-card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
  }
  
  .service-card p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .cta-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .cta-section p {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  
  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent-color);
    color: #ffffff;
  }
  
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #e0144c;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
</style>
